OL,3,C'Evil' teenager jailed for life for
OL,4,Cmurder of Elianne Andam
OL,6,FAn "evil" teenager who murdered 15-
OL,7,Fyear-old Elianne Andam in a row over a
OL,8,Fteddy bear has been sentenced to life
OL,9,Fin prison with a minimum term of 23
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FHassan Sentamu, 18, stabbed Elianne in
OL,13,Fthe neck outside the Whitgift Centre
OL,14,Fin Croydon on the way to school in
OL,15,FSeptember 2023.
OL,17,FHe had a history of attacking girls
OL,18,Fand carrying knives before he killed
OL,19,Fthe popular schoolgirl.
