OL,3,C'Evil' teenager jailed for life for
OL,4,Cmurder of Elianne Andam
OL,6,FShe told the defendant: "Elianne was
OL,7,F15 when you murdered her, she will
OL,8,Falways remain just 15, she will never
OL,9,Frealise the potential of her life."
OL,11,FThe driver for his actions was his
OL,12,F"short temper and aggressive
OL,13,Ftendencies" which combined with his
OL,14,F"deliberate decision to carry a
OL,15,Fknife," she said.
OL,17,FAs he was sent down, there were angry
OL,18,Fshouts from the public gallery
OL,19,Frejecting his earlier apology, saying:
OL,20,F"You deserve to be spat on."
