OL,6,FSentamu sat with head in his hands in
OL,7,Fthe dock and wiped away tears as he
OL,8,Fwas sentenced.
OL,10,FEarlier, Elianne's family described
OL,11,Ftheir "living nightmare" in a series
OL,12,Fof statements read to the court.
OL,14,FElianne's mother Dorcas Andam said she
OL,15,Fwas the "kindest, most loving
OL,16,Fdaughter" who was "vibrant, creative,
OL,17,Fand purposeful" and loved to sing and
OL,18,Fbraid hair.
