OL,6,FShe added: "The question that forever
OL,7,Fhaunts me is why. .. What did she ever
OL,8,Fdo to deserve such cruelty?"
OL,10,FElianne's father Michael Andam called
OL,11,Fon the judge to hand down the
OL,12,Fstrongest sentence which reflects the
OL,13,F"true horror" of what happened.
OL,15,FHe described her as a "bright light"
OL,16,Fwhose absence had left a "gaping
OL,17,Fwound".
OL,19,FHe said: "No parent should ever have
OL,20,Fto bury their child let alone in such
OL,21,Fa violent manner.
