OL,15,Fbefore school on September 27 2023.
OL,17,FAbout 10 days before, Sentamu had
OL,18,Fsplit up with Elianne's friend by
OL,19,Ftext, telling her: "Ur energy is dead
OL,20,FI'm not rdy for a relationship...all
OL,21,Fthe best."
