OL,6,FElianne stood up for her friend when
OL,7,FSentamu turned up without the bear and
OL,8,Fwalked off with a bag of his
OL,9,Fbelongings.
OL,11,FSentamu's ex-girlfriend told the
OL,12,Fcourt: "Elianne ran behind him,
OL,13,Fgrabbed the bag and started running
OL,14,Fand laughing as a joke. It was the
OL,15,Ftype of thing that Elianne would have
OL,16,Fdone.
OL,18,F"At first I was laughing a bit because
OL,19,Fit was a joke and then I got scared
OL,20,Fbecause then Hassan got mad."
