OL,3,C'Evil' teenager jailed for life for
OL,4,Cmurder of Elianne Andam
OL,6,FSentamu chased Elianne and stabbed her
OL,7,Frepeatedly as she lay on the ground `
OL,8,Fdespite her pleas for him to stop, the
OL,9,Fcourt was told.
OL,11,FShe suffered a fatal 12cm deep stab to
OL,12,Fthe neck and a passing bus driver held
OL,13,Fher hand and stayed with her as she
OL,14,Flay dying in the street.
OL,16,FThe stabbing was caught on CCTV and in
OL,17,Fthe ensuing chaos, Elianne's
OL,18,Ftraumatised friends told police what
OL,19,Fhappened and described the killer who
OL,20,Fhad fled and dumped the bloody knife.
