OL,6,FA police officer spotted him on a bus
OL,7,Fheading towards New Addington and
OL,8,Farrested him within an hour-and-a-half
OL,9,Fof the killing.
OL,11,FUganda-born Sentamu declined to give
OL,12,Fevidence in his defence, but the court
OL,13,Fwas told of his troubled childhood.
OL,15,FHe was given a police caution at the
OL,16,Fage of 12 after producing a knife in
OL,17,Fschool.
