OL,6,FOther abusive and violent behaviour
OL,7,Fincluded putting girls in a headlock,
OL,8,Fand threatening to harm a foster
OL,9,Fcarer's cat and chop off its tail.
OL,11,FThe month after Elianne's death,
OL,12,FSentamu got into a row after a fellow
OL,13,Finmate at Oakhill Secure Training
OL,14,FCentre in Milton Keynes accused him of
OL,15,Fkilling girls.
OL,17,FSentamu responded: "I'll do it again.
OL,18,FI'll do it to your mum. Do you want to
OL,19,Fend up like her, six feet under?"
