OL,6,FIn mitigation, Pavlos Panayi KC said
OL,7,Fthere were no words that could
OL,8,F"minimise, justify or excuse" such a
OL,9,F"horrific" crime.
OL,11,FReferring to Sentamu's troubled
OL,12,Fbackground, he said: "Hassan's violent
OL,13,Fstreak, his anger, his outbursts, did
OL,14,Fnot come out of nowhere. He was not
OL,15,Fborn with them. They come from his
OL,16,Flived experiences from when he was a
OL,17,Flittle boy."
